channel.title: Whats the best Ready-to-play RS2 private server
channel.description:
Oke, I like to know whats the best Ready-to-play RS2 private server.
With read-to-play, i mean: -- Tuts can easly be added -- N00bs can start it like its his/her server -- Having the most things that exists -- ... :)
I actualy think Cheezscape 80?
Just let be clear; i like to know how people think about it, i allready have my own server, i 'm not gonna take a server and start it up like its my server.
And now i would say: Vote vote vote ;D
Thx, by Mod Mopar
P.S. If you know another good server, post here, but don't post a server with added 2 thingies from an original server..
